snippet.title: Jeepney Stories Teaser
snippet.description:
Jeepney Stories is a heartwarming, slice-of-life visual novel about relationships, chance, getting old and living in the third world.

Join "Mang Paldo" in his daily adventures and conversations with people from different walks of life, culture and status. Jeepney Stories has different endings depending on how you play the game and interact with your passengers' fare. Give the incorrect change and you alter the fate of the different characters in the game and ultimately, the game's final ending.

Please wishlist on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3203470
